# Generated Xcode wrapper (produced on macOS by convert.sh) — not committed.
# convert.sh passes --app-name "Media Bulk Downloads"; the converter names the
# emitted folder after that. Ignore both the spaced form and a space-stripped
# form so the wrapper never leaks regardless of how the converter renders it.
/Media Bulk Downloads/
/MediaBulkDownloads/
*.xcodeproj/
*.xcworkspace/
build/
DerivedData/
